I actually gave a print of this to Tom King (who wrote that Batman run) and he loved it, still a highlight for me!</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gi6lOYp.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Another pic of the top portion of the dress (and me).</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EDcyiEz.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>And here’s the detail of the back of the dress! It was made by Molly Nguyen designs. I can’t sew to save my life but I really wanted to do this cosplay so I’m really grateful to her for doing such a wonderful job with it.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Z8IZdqe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[rectalpossum]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Slo-mo *BOOP*</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WUaiou2</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/QbvUuuk.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WUaiou2</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LogicDude]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Roses are red</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/PJ6H88t</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7tdSyEZ.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/PJ6H88t</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[CaptainZiploc]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Valentine's day</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lErC9OK</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/48yXkyg.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/lErC9OK</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[zalaman]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Trying on her wedding dress 60 years later</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/VOSibI5</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/lvHLVE0.gif" style=